  "title": "Tapping for calm with overflow",
  "subtitle": "A five-minute tapping script for releasing the bracing response when money is plentiful.",
  "excerpt": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 42 of the MONEY program. The script targets the habit of waiting for things to go wrong when money is good, the nervous scan for what will take it away.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Adapted from Day 42 of MONEY: A 12-Week Tapping Program (Rebecca J Page, 2025), \"Allow overflow to feel normal.\" Tapping framework: Gary Craig's Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT), in use since the mid-1990s, building on Roger Callahan's Thought Field Therapy.",
  "body": {
